title: Grateful Dead Live at Roosevelt Stadium on 1976-08-04
description:
Set I
Sugaree
New Minglewood Blues
Row Jimmy
Big River
Loser
Looks Like Rain
They Love Each Other
The Music Never Stopped
Scarlet Begonias
Set II
Help On The Way >
Slipknot! >
Franklin's Tower >
Dancing In The Street >
The Wheel >
Samson & Delilah
It Must Have Been The Roses
Not Fade Away >
Drums >
The Other One >
Ship Of Fools
Sugar Magnolia

Encore:
Johnny B. Goode


Comment
Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Keith Godchaux - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
Donna Jean Godchaux - Vocals
